column1: Specifications: "A UniFi Console designed for managing massive-scale UniFi Networks."
(1) 10G SFP+ and (1) GbE RJ45 LAN port
"Enclosure material": "Front panel: aluminium Chassis: SGCC steel"
"Networking interface": "LAN:(1) GbE RJ45 port\n(1) 10G SFP+ portMGMT LAN: (1) GbE RJ45 port"
"Ambient operating temperature": "0 to 35° C (32 to 95° F)"

"Power supply": "Off: no AC power present
Steady green: AC power and DC output active
Flashing green: AC power present and DC output inactive 
Steady amber: AC power lost/failure events
Flashing amber: warning events"
